Hey Everyone. Makar here. This map was developed after I looked at Aim_Ag_Texture2 in greater detail, I liked the different things put into it. a note, THIS MAP IS NOT AIM_AG_TEXTURE! This isn't a copy, or anything. It's completely original, and Was created in about 5 Hours or so, including Game play and testing. This map does have a few.....errors. The lights are a little bright in certain places, but not unplayable. xD

The ladders work, and although a few places may look strange, it had to be done for them to not be effected by the ladders on the wall.

For some reason, of which I cannot figure out, BOTS do NOT use ladders, thus they are useless in this map.

Have fun!

Hey guys, Here it is, the moment you've all been waiting for!!!!

UPDATE!!!!! WOOHOO!!!!!!!!

Actually, unless something arises, such as a major error or bug, this is it....sniff.

Ah well. This map has ramps, ladders a giant building with multiple levels, and rooms!
The map also has a small sniper's tower, over near the CT spawn! The map now has railings on both building roofs, is in HDR, and has more boxes, for extra fun!

The map is done! Unless someone has a comment that I really love, and want to make a change, i'm done.

Thanks!

Map made in about 5 miniutes, Press detonator shown in screenshot 1, to blow holes in wall shown in screenshot 7. You can also shoot out lights shown in screenshot 4, and it goes pitch black. So i recommend mp_flashlight 1 is on, otherwise you wont find each other. Knives and deagles are weapons allowed, please do test with other weapons and tell me which ones i should include in v2 one. Thank you and enjoy.

___ BETA 3 notes___ -Sorted the problem of spawning without Deagle. -Bot nav file included (not optimized though). ___ BETA 2 notes___ -Added lights to the map but also increased the brightness of the general lighting in the room. -Lowered the sarcophagus so you can shoot over them. -New pillars -New stairs in the alcoves -New textures -Aligned some of the old textures -Sorted some minor issues ___ BETA 1 notes___ This is a beta version of a deagle map I have been working on in between other map projects e.g. de_astute_dmw. The map has 6 spawn points for each team. I haven't spent more than 4-5 hours on it so there is still some work to do. Some textures aren't perfectly aligned or final for that matter. Still it is playable and fun. Any feedback is appreciated. The Madonna Statue is made by Hessi. Nav file and custom stuff are included in the bsp. Thanks to the people at Dead Men Walking for testing it so far. Cheers Doc

A small desert map that was designed with all weapons in mind, meaning the AWP has no advantage over the mp5. All the weapons look great with the reflections inside the buildings. A fun map to go play some quick rounds with your friends. The explosive barrels in the middle add for some extra fun if you catch someone off-gaurd. NOTE---for some reason after a reformat my computer wouldnt compile the map again, so as a result, there are a few mistakes I would fix but I can't. Those being the wire spool near the T side being off the ground and, the middle section of the glass in the 2 story building. Thanks for the download!
